  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Snow: A dream for Children of Fomeque,Colombia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">If you are living in a northern country probably you must live with snow in a period of the year (every year); but Colombia is a tropical country without seasons, we only have snow in the high Andean mountains. A recurrent childhoods dream is to know the snow.50 children (of a low-income community) in a rural school of Fomeque, Colombia, want to see the snow for the first time in their lives, a natural environment of a National Park (Los Nevados). Help us to come true this beautiful initiative!</narrative>
  </description>
